			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="40" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="After a party member opens the valve that pours lava out of on the forging platform, a golem climbs out of the pipes, attacking them.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Note: The valve can be activated by (ranged) attacks and spells, so party member positioning is not guaranteed.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Note 2: Party members who are not players can activate the valve." />
